	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Yendor</b><br /><i>Which is an indirect nerf to archery damage if being responsible for the damage we do now means we have to stop firing arrows to cast jolt unless we want to get summoned and splatted.  Funny how they manage to skirt around it like that, isn't it?<br />
