<br />
If you damage a mob it should generate a proportionate amount of hate no matter how the damage is done, or from how far away.  If you're close enough to a mob to be able to damage it, you're close enough for it to take offence.  <br />
<br />
Given the rules of proximity agro though, I also think that damage from afar should generate somewhat less hate than when it's up close.</p>
	
	
	
