	<p>The issue of DW vs. 2h was brought up.  I believe the reply was: <br />
- They're aware there may be an issue &amp; are looking into it.<br />
- They think it's related to itemization mostly.<br />
<br />
My memory of this one is hazy so I have to defer to the transcript once it's posted somewhere.<br />
<br />
Other stuff that hasn't been mentioned yet:<br />
- They know warrior taunt is broken.  They don't want warriors tied to EB weapons.  They're going to improve warrior agro generation but are working on ways to do so.  They implied it might be tied to raising skillcaps (ie, TAUNT skill).<br />
- Charm is going to be more risky.  They never got specific, but it sounds like the Test changes we've read about (though they never mentioned the exp mod).  They think charm is important and cool so don't want to nerf it into oblivion.<br />
- Monk mitigation nerf is going to be scaled back some on Tues.</p>
	
	
	
