<br />
It makes me believe that they haven't really started working on archery auto-attack or LOS issues yet. When they do finally get around to working on that stuff, it is likely to take the form of massive changes to the missile engine itself, perhaps as drastic as a complete re-write of the system.</p>
	
	
	
